{{Actor|
| type = Internal
| name = Tomed hellstaff rain tracker
| class = RainTracker
| game = Heretic
}}[[Classes]]: [[Classes:Inventory|Inventory]]&rarr;<u>RainTracker</u><br>
This stateless inventory actor keeps pointers to up to two [[Classes:RainPillar|hellstaff rains]] for a player. If a third is created, it ensures that the oldest disappears. The relevant code cannot be transcribed in [[DECORATE]] and is mostly handled by the [[Classes:HornRodFX2|projectile]]'s [[A_AddPlayerRain]] native action.

==== [[DECORATE]] definition ====
 ACTOR <u>RainTracker</u> : {{Class|Inventory}} native
 {
   +{{Flag|INVENTORY.UNDROPPABLE}}
 }
